title: 277. Andy & DJ CTI: Elon Musk's Twitter Takeover, Pregnant Inmates In NJ & Police Shooting Ft. Tommy Vext
itunes:title: 277. Andy & DJ CTI: Elon Musk's Twitter Takeover, Pregnant Inmates In NJ & Police Shooting Ft. Tommy Vext
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ get a special guest surprise in the studio by Tommy Vext. They discuss Twitter enacting a defense measure against Elon Musk's potential purchase of the social media platform, two inmates at an all-women's New Jersey jail becoming pregnant after having sex with a transgender inmate, and Grand Rapids police releasing video footage of the fatal shooting of Patrick Lyoya.
